    <!-- Application Structure Plan: 
         The app is designed as a "Executive Dashboard" rather than a linear report.
         1. Header: Brand Statement.
         2. Navigation (Pillars): Quick switching between Overview, Sportswear, Hospitality, and Fragrances.
         3. Dynamic Main Stage: The central area updates based on the selected pillar.
            - Overview: High-level metrics and Timeline.
            - Verticals: Specific product data, location maps (simulated), and category breakdowns.
         4. Data Section: Always-visible key performance indicators.
         Rationale: This structure allows users to "drill down" into the specific business arm they are interested in, 
         mirroring how an investor or brand manager would view the portfolio. -->
